{"tid":1154590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭卓堅申請覆核指陳維安涉違法讓石禮謙取代涂謹申","createTime":"2019-05-14T11:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T03:53:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f69e7d0784b828679c6d171ceaca6037053c8aa","tid":1154590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457453-20190514.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457453-20190514.htm&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=ae9a6322\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457453-20190514.htm&h=6cf153e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457453-20190514.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅申請覆核指陳維安涉違法讓石禮謙取代涂謹申<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-14 HKT 13:02<br />\n 分享工具  facebook  twitter<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1457453_1_20190514131404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1457453_1_20190514131404.jpg&h=10f813bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郭卓堅入稟高院申請司法覆核，指陳維安違反《議事規則》第四條。（陳頌慈攝）<br />\n<br />\n有「覆核王」之稱的長洲居民郭卓堅，入稟高等法院申請司法覆核，指立法會秘書長陳維安違反《議事規則》第四條，涉嫌以非法手段讓建制派議員石禮謙取代民主黨涂謹申，擔任修訂《逃犯條例》法案委員會主持的職位。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅在入稟狀指出，陳維安早前漠視議員反對，違法以書面傳閱方式表決，取消涂謹申的法案委員會主持職位，讓石禮謙取代涂謹申，要求法庭頒令判決陳維安的決定屬違法，要求法庭盡快開庭審理。"},{"pid":"308485fa54181a296223c4d6e8e942bad1df791d","tid":1154590,"uid":53498,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"等睇奶共法官又bam"},{"pid":"73dd00d683474edacd0b3e0ba5aa50d5e3d078a1","tid":1154590,"uid":158888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"告得好<br />\n陳維安食屎啦<br />\n做妹仔做到佢咁巴閉<br />\n應該炒佢"},{"pid":"4827dc4754110e4acc09cda10b715e46a33aaca8","tid":1154590,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"郭伯伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8080d55662f9a2f8f57903e950dcf8eb67412685","tid":1154590,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rRH9ndz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrRH9ndz.png&h=1a176042&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}